{"article_id":"92Bs3dzBOYW7DjVY","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Marie Yovanovitch told lawmakers","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"she had only U.S. interests in mind","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"while serving as ambassador to Ukraine at an impeachment inquiry hearing Friday","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"during which President Donald Trump tweeted insults at her .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Yovanovitch , 61 , also responded to debunked GOP claims","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"that Ukraine meddled in the 2016 U.S. elections ,","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"and agreed","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"that the military aid","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"the Trump administration endorsed","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"- and is now at the heart of the investigation -","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"has benefited the Eastern European country in its war against Russia .","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Yovanovitch ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"recalled as ambassador in May","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"after falling out of Trump 's favor ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"is a key witness in the House impeachment inquiry into the president 's efforts","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"to pressure the East European country to investigate his political rivals .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Friday 's open session before the House Intelligence Committee was the second public hearing of the inquiry","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"following testimony Wednesday by veteran diplomats Bill Taylor George Kent .","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"Not long after the hearing began ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Trump began tweeting critically about Yovanovitch","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"as she was testifying about the `` smear ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"campaign administration officials had waged","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"that led to her ouster in May .","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"The hearing lasted about five hours","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"with Democrats trying to show","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"that Trump removed Yovanovitch","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to make it easier for his allies to pursue political goals","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and Republicans saying","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"U.S. policy toward Ukraine improved","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"after Trump became president .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"During her testimony , the ambassador tried to portray herself as a straight shooter","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"whose top priority was carrying out U.S. priorities .","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"`` I entered the Foreign Service understanding","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"that my job was to implement the foreign policy interests of this nation ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"as defined by the President and Congress ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"and to do so","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"regardless of which person or party was in power , ''","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"she told lawmakers .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"`` I had no agenda","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"other than to pursue our stated foreign policy goals . ''","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Later under questioning , Yovanovitch said","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"she was `` shocked , appalled , devastated ''","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"when she learned in September","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"that Trump in a July 25 call to Ukraine President Volodymyr Zelensky described her as `` bad news . ''","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"She said","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"she found the charge startling","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"because she did nothing","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to undermine U.S. interests under Trump .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Trump has tweeted his criticism of the inquiry dozens of times","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"since the impeachment process began several weeks ago .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"But his scorching tweets during Yovanovitch 's testimony took center stage at one point .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"A little more than an hour into the testimony , Democratic staff displayed two of the tweets on large screens in the hearing room","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"as Schiff read them aloud :","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"I have such powers , ''","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"Yovanovitch said","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"when Schiff asked for her reaction to the tweets .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"`` It 's very intimidating . ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"`` I want you to know","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"that some of us here take witness intimidation very very seriously , ''","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"Schiff responded .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Yovanovitch described as `` really positive '' and `` really generous '' that , at the urging of the Trump administration , Congress approved hundreds of millions in military assistance .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"Much of that money was for Javelins , portable anti-tank missiles .","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"`` So","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"if the war with Russia all of a sudden accelerated in some way","depth":15},{"id":66,"text":"and tanks come over the horizon ,","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"javelins are a very serious weapon","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"to deal with that , ''","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"she told lawmakers","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"when asked by Republican Counsel Steve Castor about the importance of the aid .","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"`` But really the more important issue is the symbolism of it ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"that the United States is providing javelins to Ukraine","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"and that makes Ukraine 's adversaries think twice . ''","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"The delivery of lethal aid ,","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"rejected under Obama ,","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"has been a steady talking point from Republicans","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"who said","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Trump acted to help the Eastern European country in its war with Russia","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"when the previous administration would n't .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"But Yovanovitch also criticized the mixed signals","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"sent by the Trump administration 's hold-up of the aid , a 55-day period earlier this year","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that stretched from July 18 to Sept. 11 .","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"`` When there are questions","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"as to whether or not our security assistance is going to go through ,","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"that kind of undermines that strong message of support , ''","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Much like they did with Wednesday 's witnesses , Bill Taylor and George Kent ,","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"Democrats made a point","depth":13},{"id":89,"text":"of stressing the integrity of Yovanovitch , a career diplomat","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"whose Ukraine posting was her third stint as an ambassador .","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"Intelligence Committee Chairman Adam Schiff , D-Calif. , praised Yovanovitch during her 33 years in the State Department","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"for earning a reputation","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"for fighting corruption","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"and naming names .","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"She had arrived in the United States","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"after her parents fled the Soviet Union and Nazi Germany ,","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"Schiff said .","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"But Yovanovitch was recalled in April ,","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"despite being offered an extension of her tour by the State Department ,","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"and told President Donald Trump had lost confidence in her ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"Schiff said .","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"First hearing :","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"New revelations , steady witnesses , Trump tweets :","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"takeaways from the first public hearing on impeachment","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"\" It was a stunning turn of events for this highly regarded career diplomat ,","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"who had been doing such a remarkable job","depth":15},{"id":107,"text":"fighting corruption in Ukraine","depth":15},{"id":108,"text":"that a short time earlier she had been asked by the State Department to extend her tour , \"","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"Schiff said .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"`` All Americans are deeply in your debt , ''","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"Schiff later told her .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"Yovanovitch also tried to swat down claims by Republicans","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"that Ukraine was at the heart of a foreign interference campaign in the 2016 election","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"aimed at hurting Trump 's election .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"`` Our own U.S. Intelligence Community has conclusively determined","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"that those","depth":14},{"id":117,"text":"who interfered in","depth":15},{"id":118,"text":"the ( 2016 )","depth":16},{"id":119,"text":"election","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"were in Russia , ''","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"she told lawmakers .","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"Russia 's aggressive meddling ,","depth":13},{"id":123,"text":"including its efforts","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"to help","depth":16},{"id":125,"text":"- not hurt -","depth":16},{"id":126,"text":"Trump ,","depth":15},{"id":127,"text":"was well documented in special counsel Robert Mueller 's report on Russian election meddling","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"that came out earlier this year .","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"Yovanovitch said","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"that Ukrainian officials","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"who criticized Trump during the 2016 election","depth":14},{"id":132,"text":"did not constitute a `` plan or a plot '' against him .","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"Echoing a familiar mantra ,","depth":10},{"id":134,"text":"Republicans said","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"the impeachment inquiry is stymieing Congress ' work on a range of issues","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"including trade agreements","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"and avoiding a government shutdown .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"`` It 's unfortunate that today and for most of next week we will continue engaging in the Democrats ' day-long TV spectacles","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"instead of solving the problems","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"we were all sent to Washington","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"to address , ''","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"California Rep. Devin Nunes , the top Republican on the committee , said .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"`` We now have a major trade agreement with Canada and Mexico ready for approval , a deal","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"that would create jobs","depth":13},{"id":145,"text":"and boost our economy , ''","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"he continued .","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"`` Meanwhile , we have not yet approved funding for the government ,","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"which expires next week .","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"along with funding for our men and women in uniform .","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"Instead , the Democrats have convened us once again","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"to advance their operation","depth":13},{"id":152,"text":"to topple a duly elected president . ''","depth":13},{"id":153,"text":"Democrats","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"who control the House","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"say","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"the criticism is hollow","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"considering the House has passed","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"- and keeps passing -","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"important legislation , such as bills","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"to help veterans ,","depth":11},{"id":161,"text":"that the GOP-run Senate refuses to take up .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"And House Speaker Nancy Pelosi said","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"the impeachment inquiry is n't stopping the House from working on trade agreements , prescription drug prices and efforts","depth":9},{"id":164,"text":"to keep the government open .","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"`` So","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"as I say ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"we legislate .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"We investigate ...","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"But we litigate , ''","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"she told reporters Thursday .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":341,"left":0,"right":340,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":340,"left":181,"right":339,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":181,"left":174,"right":180,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":1,"right":173,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":173,"left":172,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":172,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":175,"right":179,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":7,"right":178,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":178,"left":177,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":177,"left":8,"right":176,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":176,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":339,"left":199,"right":338,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":185,"right":198,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":185,"left":183,"right":184,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":183,"left":12,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":184,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":191,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuc